OL,5, A takeaway owner is offering to give   
OL,6, everyone in Edinburgh a free pizza over
OL,7, the next month as an act of kindness.  
OL,9,FMarc Wilkinson, 55, the owner of Pure  
OL,10,FPizza in Morningside, said he had been 
OL,11,Fplanning a big altruistic act to help  
OL,12,Fpeople struggling with the cost of     
OL,13,Fliving crisis.                         
OL,15,FHe said it would also give his         
OL,16,Fpart-time staff more work.             
OL,18,F"I'm very happy with my plan because   
OL,19,Fit's a win, win, win for everyone," he 
OL,20,Fsaid.                                  
